1. Initialize SQLite database on app launch using expo-sqlite
2. Create these tables on init:
   - field_measurements (matches FieldMeasurement interface)
   - checklist_entries (matches ChecklistEntry interface)
   - freeform_notes (matches FreeformNote interface)
   - sync_queue (matches SyncQueueItem interface — this is the offline buffer)

3. Implement typed functions:
   - insertFieldMeasurement(record: FieldMeasurement): Promise<void>
   - insertChecklistEntry(record: ChecklistEntry): Promise<void>
   - insertFreeformNote(record: FreeformNote): Promise<void>
   - getAllUnsynced(): Promise<SyncQueueItem[]>
   - markSynced(id: string): Promise<void>
